          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_Membership_GetAllUsers",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve a paginated list of users from an ASP.NET membership database for a specified application. It uses the application name to filter users and returns user details such as username, email, and various membership-related information. The procedure also calculates the total number of users for the application and returns this count as the procedure's return value."
        }
