                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Security",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Ensure that input parameters are validated to prevent SQL injection, although parameterized queries mitigate this risk."
